title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Subus Wit Da Titties Out
description:
Sometimes the Fit Check is the podcast. That’s how you know it’s good. The Core 4 are back on their bullshit, leaving no tangent unexplored and meandering like it’s their goddamn job because, well, it is. From male grooming and supply chain breakdowns to Roomba attempted suicide and Yohji Yamamoto, this one really has it all, including Jimmy and Larry’s latest fight that leaves the groms painfully speechless.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits
